{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.selfTime\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">selfTime</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Appends the number of milliseconds spent inside each subtree but outside of its child nodes to\nthe subtree's head message. Timing information is only available with\n`set_option trace.profiler true`; nodes without it are not annotated.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.selfTime","kind":"def","line":437,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.selfTime","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L437-L451"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.countNodes\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">countNodes</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Appends the number of nodes inside each subtree to the subtree's head message. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.countNodes","kind":"def","line":419,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.countNodes","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L419-L430"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.exposeSubtrees\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">exposeSubtrees</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Expands all transitive ancestors of the subtrees matching `p` in the editor, so that the trace\nopens already showing all matches. No nodes are removed, and all other nodes, including the\nmatches themselves, keep their expansion state. Matching subtrees are not searched for nested\nmatches.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.exposeSubtrees","kind":"def","line":401,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.exposeSubtrees","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L401-L417"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.hoist\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">hoist</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Hoists the subtrees matching `p` to the top level, so that every new trace root is a match;\nancestors and unrelated subtrees are discarded. Matches nested inside other matches are not\nsearched for.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.hoist","kind":"def","line":393,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.hoist","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L393-L399"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.filterSubtrees\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterSubtrees</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Keeps only the subtrees matching `p`, together with their ancestors for context; all other nodes\nare removed. Matching subtrees are kept in their entirety and not searched for nested matches\n(see `TraceTree.filterSubtrees`).\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.filterSubtrees","kind":"def","line":385,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.filterSubtrees","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L385-L391"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.minSelfTimeMs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">minSelfTimeMs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ms</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Float.html#Float\">Float</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the subtrees whose action took at least `ms` milliseconds outside of their child nodes.\nTiming information is only available with `set_option trace.profiler true`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.minSelfTimeMs","kind":"def","line":374,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.minSelfTimeMs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L374-L379"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.minTimeMs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">minTimeMs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ms</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Float.html#Float\">Float</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the subtrees whose action took at least `ms` milliseconds.\nTiming information is only available with `set_option trace.profiler true`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.minTimeMs","kind":"def","line":367,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.minTimeMs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L367-L372"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.unsuccessful\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">unsuccessful</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the trace nodes whose action did not succeed, i.e. failed (❌️) or threw an exception\n(💥️). Nodes without a recorded result (e.g. from `addTrace`) do not match.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.unsuccessful","kind":"def","line":360,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.unsuccessful","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L360-L365"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.errored\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">errored</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the trace nodes whose action threw an exception (💥️, `TraceResult.error`). ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.errored","kind":"def","line":356,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.errored","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L356-L358"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.failed\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">failed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the trace nodes whose action failed (❌️, `TraceResult.failure`). ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.failed","kind":"def","line":352,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.failed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L352-L354"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.succeeded\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">succeeded</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the trace nodes whose action succeeded (✅️, `TraceResult.success`).\nNodes without a recorded result (e.g. from `addTrace`) do not match.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.succeeded","kind":"def","line":345,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.succeeded","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L345-L350"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.containsString\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">containsString</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pat</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the subtrees whose trace class or head message contains `pat` as a substring.\nFor large traces, this is an expensive pattern because all head messages need to be\npretty-printed; to select nodes by their exact trace class, prefer the much cheaper `ofClass`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.containsString","kind":"def","line":335,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.containsString","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L335-L343"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.ofClass\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofClass</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">cls</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Matches the trace nodes with the exact trace class `cls`. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.ofClass","kind":"def","line":331,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.ofClass","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L331-L333"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.filterSubtrees\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterSubtrees</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Prunes the tree to the subtrees satisfying `p`, keeping their ancestors for context; `none` if\nthere is no match. The resulting tree consists of those nodes that either have a matching\nancestor or transitive child. Matching subtrees are not searched for nested matches.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.filterSubtrees","kind":"opaque","line":310,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.filterSubtrees","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L310-L322"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.collectSubtrees\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">collectSubtrees</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\">TracePattern</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">acc</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">#[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Collects all maximal subtrees satisfying `p` in `acc`: adds `t` itself if `p t` holds, and\notherwise recurses into the children. Matching subtrees are not searched for nested matches.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.collectSubtrees","kind":"opaque","line":300,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.collectSubtrees","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L300-L308"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.result?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">result?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.TraceResult\">TraceResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `TraceResult` of a trace node; `none` for leaf messages and nodes without a result. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.result?","kind":"def","line":296,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.result?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L296-L298"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.headText\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">headText</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#BaseIO\">BaseIO</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The message of this node (without its children), formatted as a string.\nUseful for text-based filters but expensive.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.headText","kind":"def","line":284,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.headText","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L284-L294"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.selfElapsed\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">selfElapsed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Float.html#Float\">Float</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elapsed time of this node that is not accounted for by its children, in seconds; `0` if no\nprofiling data is available.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.selfElapsed","kind":"def","line":277,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.selfElapsed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L277-L282"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.elapsed\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">elapsed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Float/Float.html#Float\">Float</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elapsed time of this node in seconds; `0` if no profiling data is available. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.elapsed","kind":"def","line":271,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.elapsed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L271-L275"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.modifyData\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">modifyData</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.TraceData\">TraceData</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.TraceData\">TraceData</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Transforms the `TraceData` of a trace node. Leaf messages are returned unchanged. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.modifyData","kind":"def","line":265,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.modifyData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L265-L269"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.withChildren\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">withChildren</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">children</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Replaces the children of a trace node. Leaf messages are returned unchanged. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.withChildren","kind":"def","line":259,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.withChildren","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L259-L263"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.children\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">children</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The children of this tree. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.children","kind":"def","line":254,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.children","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L254-L257"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.cls?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">cls?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">t</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The trace class of a trace node; `none` for leaf messages. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.cls?","kind":"def","line":250,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.cls?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L250-L252"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.data?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">data?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.TraceData\">TraceData</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `TraceData` of a trace node; `none` for leaf messages. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.data?","kind":"def","line":245,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.data?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L245-L248"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TracePattern</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A pattern selects the trace subtrees that an operation acts on (see `filter`, `hoist`, and\n`expand`). Patterns are ordinary predicates: the built-in ones (such as `containsString`,\n`unsuccessful`, or `minTimeMs`) can be combined with custom conditions in a `fun`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern","kind":"def","line":236,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePattern","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L236-L241"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.PostprocessTraces.elabPostprocessTraces\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabPostprocessTraces</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElab\">Command.CommandElab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.PostprocessTraces.elabPostprocessTraces","kind":"def","line":212,"name":"Lean.Elab.PostprocessTraces.elabPostprocessTraces","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L212-L230"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTracePostprocessor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedTracePostprocessor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\">TracePostprocessor</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTracePostprocessor","kind":"instance","line":117,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTracePostprocessor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L117-L117"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TracePostprocessor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A trace postprocessor transforms the trace roots of a trace message before it is reported,\ne.g. by filtering out irrelevant subtrees or pre-expanding interesting nodes.\nReturning an empty array drops the trace message entirely.\n\nTraces are reported as one message per source range inside a command, and a postprocessor is\napplied to each of these messages separately; it therefore cannot move trace roots from one\nsource range to another.\n\nPostprocessors are applied by the `postprocess_traces post in cmd` command and can be composed\nleft-to-right with `>=>`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor","kind":"def","line":103,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L103-L115"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.toMessageData\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">toMessageData</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reassembles the `MessageData` of a trace tree. ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.toMessageData","kind":"opaque","line":98,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.toMessageData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L98-L101"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.ofMessageData\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofMessageData</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">msg</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Decomposes trace `MessageData` into a `TraceTree`. The `MessageData` can be reconstructed using\n`TraceTree.toMessageData`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.ofMessageData","kind":"def","line":85,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.ofMessageData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L85-L96"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTraceTree\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedTraceTree</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTraceTree","kind":"instance","line":83,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTraceTree","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L83-L83"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.leaf\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">leaf</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">msg</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A child message that is not itself a trace node (e.g. produced by `addRawTrace`). ","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.leaf","kind":"ctor","line":80,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.leaf","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L80-L81"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.node\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span>.<span class=\"name\">node</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">data</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.TraceData\">TraceData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">msg</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">children</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">wrap</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\">TraceTree</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A trace node `[data.cls] msg` with the given children.\n\n`wrap` restores the context wrappers (`MessageData.withContext` etc.) that were peeled off the\noriginal `MessageData` while decomposing it; it is re-applied around the node by\n`toMessageData`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.node","kind":"ctor","line":71,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree.node","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L71-L79"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">TraceTree</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A structured view of a trace message (`MessageData.trace`), used by trace postprocessors\n(see `TracePostprocessor`).\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree","kind":"inductive","line":66,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L66-L81"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.postprocessTracesCmd\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PostprocessTraces</span>.<span class=\"name\">postprocessTracesCmd</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Experimental. `postprocess_traces` and the library around it are expected to change in the future.\n\n`postprocess_traces post in cmd` runs `cmd` and transforms every trace message it produces\nwith the trace postprocessor `post : Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor` before it is reported.\n\nThe postprocessor receives the array of trace roots of each trace message and returns the\ntransformed roots; returning an empty array drops the message entirely. The `Lean.PostprocessTraces`\nnamespace (automatically opened in `post`) provides operations such as `filterSubtrees`, `hoist`,\n`exposeSubtrees`, and `selfTime`, which take patterns such as `ofClass`, `containsString`, and\n`minTimeMs` and compose left-to-right with `>=>`. User-defined postprocessors and patterns are\nordinary functions.\n\nFor example, the following only shows the instance-synthesis steps that mention `tryResolve`,\ntogether with their ancestors:\n```lean\nset_option trace.Meta.synthInstance true in\npostprocess_traces filter (containsString \"tryResolve\") in\nexample : Inhabited (List Nat) := inferInstance\n```\n","docLink":"./Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.html#Lean.PostprocessTraces.postprocessTracesCmd","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.postprocessTracesCmd","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/PostprocessTraces/Basic.lean#L42-L64"}}],"imports":["Lean.CoreM","Lean.Elab.Command","Lean.Meta.Eval"],"instances":[{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTraceTree","typeNames":["Lean.PostprocessTraces.TraceTree"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.instInhabitedTracePostprocessor","typeNames":["Lean.PostprocessTraces.TracePostprocessor"]}],"name":"Lean.PostprocessTraces.Basic"}